{"tid":1360633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邏輯討論：後面有冇大台","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T13:42:08.000Z","uid":112146,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f1031a59e8f0e8a4a8cd035badb152ccd3b6da3c","tid":1360633,"uid":112146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"我有啲困惑，想大家指點下我<br />\n<br />\n我見啲老人家成日話我哋後面有大台，我由六月頭行到今日，我都唔知我哋個大台係邊個，我確實相信我哋係冇大台<br />\n<br />\n咁但係佢哋又一口咬定我哋有大台，咁佢都用咗成個月嘅時間啦，都搵唔到咩證據<br />\n正常我就應該話搵唔到咪即係冇囉<br />\n<br />\n但係係咪搵唔到就會相信冇呢，又好似唔合邏輯<br />\n如果咁易放棄自己嘅信念，呢個世界啲科研就搞唔到落去，佢咁樣堅持自己嘅信念又唔係錯得晒<br />\n<br />\n情況就好似你信唔信有外星人一樣，我話我真係睇唔到，你又求其執啲理由返嚟話有外星人，咁我都真係唔知點解釋比佢哋聽<br />\n<br />\n情況又好似啲人話有冇鬼一樣，有啲人見到，有啲人又見唔到<br />\n要殺再攞啲證據出嚟又冇<br />\n咁叫有定無呢<br />\n<br />\n我都真係唔知邊個先啱<br />\n邏輯有啲混亂，希望有人可以屌醒我"},{"pid":"1324d1101d5eb03d9f4c0ceeb2ecae469478f009","tid":1360633,"uid":203889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5-%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3-18-%E7%A8%AE%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E6%2594%25BB%25E7%2595%25A5-%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3-18-%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%2F&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9beFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=e745cb1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E6%2594%25BB%25E7%2595%25A5-%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3-18-%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%2F&h=fe61f583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5-%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3-18-%E7%A8%AE%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇熟佢"},{"pid":"4def020f34815410e2c815f82f5e7c91a12ba95b","tid":1360633,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:39:38.000Z","msg":"問番佢邊個有號召力可以做大台呀嗎<br />\n一次都冇露過面都搞到成個月"},{"pid":"1dad3b3ce38c1474d994c03bf0188bff4c9e9885","tid":1360633,"uid":97267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"因為老人家唔相信共同信念 佢地唔會理解冇大台組織既群眾活動"},{"pid":"c5246c7841ad6f3c724af5a7695eafac07f6737b","tid":1360633,"uid":270730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}